rows.label: tlk43600142_01_msg0002
rows.name:
We were so close to open war with
Superbia, but it was averted at
the last moment.

rows.label: tlk43600142_01_msg0003
rows.name:
It would have been my big chance to
rake in the big bucks...

rows.label: tlk43600142_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Lending money to injured soldiers,
bereaving widows... There's really
nothing like wartime profits.

rows.label: tlk43600142_01_msg0005
rows.name: Just whose side is Her Majesty on?
